title: Łączna, Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship
text:
Łączna is a <a href="village">village</a> in <a href="Skar%C5%BCysko%20County">Skarżysko County</a>, <a href="%C5%9Awi%C4%99tokrzyskie%20Voivodeship">Świętokrzyskie Voivodeship</a>, in south-central <a href="Poland">Poland</a>. It is the seat of the <a href="gmina">gmina</a> (administrative district) called <a href="Gmina%20%C5%81%C4%85czna">Gmina Łączna</a>. It lies approximately south-west of <a href="Skar%C5%BCysko-Kamienna">Skarżysko-Kamienna</a> and north-east of the regional capital <a href="Kielce">Kielce</a>.
The village has a population of 780.
